<pb n="0062a" id="I01.0024.0062a" ed="I"/>
<lb ed="C I" n="0062a00"/><milestone n="1" unit="juan"/><head type="no">No. 24</head>
<lb ed="C I" n="0062a00"/><juan n="001" fun="open"><mulu n="001" type="卷"/><jhead><title>仇臣生造像記</title></jhead></juan>
<lb ed="C I" n="0062a01"/><p id="pI01p0062a0101">正光五年歲次甲辰七月己酉朔十五日<note n="0062001" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30495;＝癸【史】</note><app n="0062001"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">癸</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30495;</rdg></app>亥。
<lb ed="C I" n="0062a02"/>雍州北地三原縣仇臣生。值遇上世。信心三寶。
<lb ed="C I" n="0062a03"/>造石像一<note n="0062002" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30496;＝區【史】</note><app n="0062002"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">區</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30496;</rdg></app>。上為皇帝陛下。州郡令長。七世父
<lb ed="C I" n="0062a04"/>母。願上生天上。值遇諸佛。下隧人間。侯王長者
<lb ed="C I" n="0062a05"/>之家。現世之報。延年益壽。子孫興隆。<note n="0062003" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30355;＝所【史】</note><app n="0062003"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">所</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30355;</rdg></app>願如<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">斯</unclear>
<lb ed="C I" n="0062a06"/>夫信欲稱善者。非至德不顯其功。欲游嵩岳者。
<lb ed="C I" n="0062a07"/>非空寂<note n="0062004" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30478;＝亦【史】</note><app n="0062004"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">亦</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30478;</rdg></app>不達其<app source="0062003" type="＊"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">所</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30355;</rdg></app>。昔太子絕思於龍<note n="0062005" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30497;＝華【史】</note><app n="0062005"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">華</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30497;</rdg></app>。身<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">體</unclear>
<lb ed="C I" n="0062a08"/>如來之<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">願</unclear>。月<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">辰</unclear>叩白駒而脩禮。<app source="0062004" type="＊"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">亦</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30478;</rdg></app>蒙神道之助。
<lb ed="C I" n="0062a09"/>是以積善成道。累<note n="0062006" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30498;＝惡【史】</note><app n="0062006"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">惡</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30498;</rdg></app><note n="0062007" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30499;＝滅【史】</note><app n="0062007"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">滅</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30499;</rdg></app>身。宜斑經藉。流芳來葉。
<lb ed="C I" n="0062a10"/>不敢多進。　　親祖仇收　忘父仇進興
<lb ed="C I" n="0062a11"/>　　　　　　　　　　　忘叔仇<note n="0062008" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30500;＝歸【史】</note><app n="0062008"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">歸</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30500;</rdg></app>興</p>
